{
  "id": "adv_event_2302_01_04",
  "title": "相思相愛\nチョコレート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、今日は収録お疲れ様\nこの後は仕事もないし、帰宅しても大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job on the recording today‚ both of you.\nYou don't have any more work after this‚ so you can go home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.9467121125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい\nそれなら、遅くならないうちに帰りましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright.\nIn that case‚ let's head home before it gets too late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1333333333,
      "endTime": 11.6235374768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 11.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事で疲れた瑠依ちゃんの帰りを\n待っとかなあかんし……うふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to wait for Rui-chan\nwho's tired from work… hehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8333333333,
      "endTime": 17.7278457959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん、CMの一件以来\nますます瑠依ちゃんガチ勢が加速してるような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ ever since the thing with the CM‚\nIt feels like passion for Rui-chan is accelerating more and more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9333333333,
      "endTime": 24.8478004773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、仲がいいのは悪いことじゃないだろう\nどこかと比べてる訳じゃないけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ having a close relationship isn't a bad thing.\nIt's not like comparing them to anyone else…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333333333,
      "endTime": 30.8551700909,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11899.999999999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、俺は次の現場があるから\n送ってあげられなくてごめん。また明日な",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I have another job coming up‚\nso I can't give you a ride. Sorry. See you tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4666666667,
      "endTime": 37.958594099799996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5666648864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "さて、うちらも行こか\n……うん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's go too.\n…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5666648864,
      "endTime": 42.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 42.9999977111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？　楽屋の外に誰かいた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong? Is there someone outside the dressing room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9999977111,
      "endTime": 46.6504513263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8666643778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "今のは……まさか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8666643778,
      "endTime": 49.971970574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.1999977111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……あそこにおるんは、例の俳優さんやな\n仕事終わりっぽいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it… that person over there is the actor we know.\nIt seems like he's done with work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2666643778,
      "endTime": 59.074646154999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.2666643778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "本当だ、せっかくだしご挨拶していこうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's true. Since he's here‚ should we go say hi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2666643778,
      "endTime": 63.3398162523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5333310444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてんの！\n瑠依ちゃんの唇奪おうとしてる、うちらの敵やんか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about!\nHe's our enemy‚ trying to steal Rui-chan's lips!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5333310444,
      "endTime": 68.9417890865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1333310444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "うちらの……って、一括りにされてる\n俳優さんが奪いたいんじゃなくて、そういうCMなだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our enemy…? Hey‚ don't lump me in with that.\nThe actor doesn't want to steal anything; it's just part of the CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1333310444,
      "endTime": 77.89743569679999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.0999977111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "細かいツッコミはええからっ\nこうなったらプランB…………追いかけます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't care in the details.\nIf it's come to this‚ we'll go with Plan B… and follow him!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0999977111,
      "endTime": 84.33557605739999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7733.3333332999955
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.5666643778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、やっぱりやめておこうよ……\n尾行して、不祥事の決定的瞬間を撮る、なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ maybe we should stop here…\nStalking him and capturing a crucial moment of a scandal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5333310444,
      "endTime": 95.9084786732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3333310444
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3666643778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、やめへん……これはうちがやらなあかん仕事！\nすみれちゃんは帰っとき……手と心が汚れてまうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we can't back down… this is a job that we must do!\nSumire-chan‚ you should go home… because your hands and heart might get dirty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3666643778,
      "endTime": 105.80993010200001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.6666643778
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9999977111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、私がついて来てるのは\n優ちゃんが暴走して罪を犯さないよう監視……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm here to make sure Yu-chan doesn't go\nout of control and commit a crime… oh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9999977111,
      "endTime": 112.88791170100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.9021415579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "あの横断歩道渡ってるお婆ちゃん、大丈夫かな\nゆっくり歩いてるけど、もうすぐ信号変わっちゃう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That old lady crossing the street‚ is she okay?\nShe's walking slowly‚ but the traffic lights are about to change…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2333310444,
      "endTime": 122.0333310444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.2333264668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまやな……\n尾行はいったんやめて、手伝いに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right…\nLet's stop the stalking for now and help her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2333264668,
      "endTime": 126.9371586163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.0999931335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、待って\nさっきの俳優さん、なんや声掛けてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ though…\nThat actor from earlier‚ he's talking to her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0999931335,
      "endTime": 133.30527658460002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4999931335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、一緒に渡ってあげてるんだ\n車が飛び出してこないように……いい人なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I see. He's helping her cross the street.\nMaking sure no cars come by… he's a good person‚ isn't he?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4999931335,
      "endTime": 142.5260244369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
