      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 281.466675059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃん……！\nあ、あのな！　うちも渡したい物があるんです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan…!\nWait! I also have something to give you…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.466675059,
      "endTime": 287.7973291443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 289.1000083923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "その後、うちのチョコだけは受け取ってくれてな\nああ、うちらは相思相愛やんな～って思ったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ she was the one who only accepted my chocolate.\nAh‚ we were madly in love back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.166675059,
      "endTime": 299.7391809463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 294.866675059
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 299.9333417256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "へえ……その頃の優ちゃんは、まだ純粋だったんだ……\nなんだか、凄くステキなお話、聞けちゃったな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ really… Back in those days‚ Yu-chan was still so pure…\nSomehow‚ I got to hear such a wonderful story!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.9333417256,
      "endTime": 311.18613583449996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 307.566675059
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 311.366675059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "その頃ってのが気になるけど……せやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm curious about \"back in those days‚\" but… you know what I mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.366675059,
      "endTime": 315.5776273886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん今後、瑠依ちゃんの前に\nめっっちゃステキな人が現れたら、応援してあげたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ from now on‚ if an incredibly wonderful person\nappears before Rui-chan‚ I want to support her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.066675059,
      "endTime": 322.4089775085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 322.7333417256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、うちがトリエルの一員としてそばにいるうちは\n厄介な人間は誰一人近づけさせへん……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as long as I'm part of TRINITYAiLE‚\nI won't let any troublesome people get close…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.7333417256,
      "endTime": 330.3108612039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 330.7000083923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "例えそれが、うちの愛の押しつけであっても……\n瑠依ちゃんの……トリエルのためになるはずやから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it means pushing my love onto her…\nthis is for Rui-chan… for the sake of TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.7000083923,
      "endTime": 339.0313306504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 339.2333417256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん……\nごめん、私も間違ってたかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan…\nI'm sorry. I might have been mistaken too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.2333417256,
      "endTime": 346.9929951621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 347.2000083923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな想いがあって\n優ちゃんは瑠依ちゃんの唇を守ろうとしてたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With those feelings‚\nyou were trying to protect Rui-chan's lips‚ weren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.2000083923,
      "endTime": 352.2264283229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 352.6000083923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_04-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "……そういうことなら、私も誓いを立てるよ\n二人目の『瑠依ちゃんの唇守り隊』隊員として！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If that's the case‚ I'll make a pledge too.\nAs the second member of the \"Rui-chan's Lip Protection Squad\"!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.6000083923,
      "endTime": 360.98370836099997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 361.166675059
    },
    {
